endbox.com/blog/virmach-first-month-free-vps-1month-after-and-more-starting-at-1-95month-for-128mb-in-buffalo/\">last featured</a>. To celebrate their anniversary, they are sharing three KVM offers for all the LowEndBox readers. The service is located in Buffalo, NY with ColoCrossing. Free DDoS protection is in place and Windows license is included for some configurations. Congratulations to VirMach and may you have many more anniversaries to come!</p><p>Host nodes used for this offer have 2x Intel Xeon E5-2620 v2 CPU, 128GB RAM, 4x 1TB SSD BBU in Hardware RAID10, 1Gbps uplink, and 10Gbps DDoS Protection. The RAID10 SSD disk configuration should give customers good disk performance!</p><p><strong>The offers</strong></p><table><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><strong>SSD512 KVM</strong><p></p><ul><li>512MB RAM</li><li>1x CPU core</li><li>5GB SSD space</li><li>1TB transfer</li><li>1Gbps uplink</li><li>10Gbps DDoS Protection</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>KVM/SolusVM</li><li>Coupon: <strong>LEB512</strong></li><li>$20/year</li><li><a href=\"https://virmach.com/manage/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=81&amp;promocode=LEB512\">Order here</a></li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong>SSD1G KVM</strong><p></p><ul><li>1GB RAM</li><li>1x CPU core</li><li>15GB SSD space</li><li>1TB transfer</li><li>1Gbps uplink</li><li>10Gbps DDoS Protection</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>Linux or Windows (Licensed, Free)</li><li>KVM/SolusVM</li><li>Coupon: <strong>LEB1GB</strong></li><li>$4.50/month</li><li><a href=\"https://virmach.com/manage/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=82&amp;promocode=LEB1GB\">Order here</a></li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong>SSD2G KVM</strong><p></p><ul><li>2GB RAM</li><li>1x CPU core</li><li>20GB SSD space</li><li>2TB transfer</li><li>1Gbps uplink</li><li>10Gbps DDoS Protection</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>Linux or Windows (Licensed, Free)</li><li>KVM/SolusVM</li><li>Coupon: <strong>LEB2GB</strong></li><li>$7/month</li><li><a href=\"https://virmach.com/manage/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=83&amp;promocode=LEB2GB\">Order here</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p>VirMach is a US-based VPS company that was established last year (2014). They are a registered LLC with registration ID 3512454410. Their services are managed by a small team of 3 people. One of their very first servers was <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/virmach-first-month-free-vps-1month-after-and-more-starting-at-1-95month-for-128mb-in-buffalo/\">featured</a> here in LowEndBox. Since then, they now expanded their service \u2013 KVM and Windows are now available. We would appreciate if you will share your feedback at the comments section below.</p><p><span id=\"more-7868\"></span></p><p>VirMach accepts payments via PayPal, Credit/Debit, BitCoin. There is a 24 hours refund policy in place, but with some restrictions. They have a strict no-spam policy, so you may not use their servers to mass mail, or spam referral links. As always, kindly read their full <a href=\"http://virmach.com/terms-conditions/\">Terms of Service</a> before making any purchase.</p><p><strong>Network Information</strong></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">ColoCrossing \u2013 Buffalo, New York, USA</span><br>\nTest IPv4: 107.173.176.5<br>\nTest file: <a href=\"https://lg.virmach.com/100MB.test\">https://lg.virmach.com/100MB.test</a><br>\nLooking glass: <a href=\"https://lg.virmach.com/\">https://lg.virmach.com/</a></p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fvirmach-20year-512mb-kvm-vps-and-more-in-buffalo-ny-usa%2F&amp;t=VirMach%20-%2